<h2 id="tables-and-lists">Tables and Lists <a class="headerlink" href="console-styling#tables-and-lists" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>The <code>SymfonyStyle</code> has helpers for a few other things, like progress bars and tables.
